%% Pudel Admin Mutual RSA Authentication Flow v2.1.1
%% Each admin has their own RSA keypair for mutual authentication

sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Admin User
    participant Browser as Browser (Vue)
    participant API as Pudel API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Discord as Discord OAuth2

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 1: Discord OAuth Login (Required First)

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Login with Discord"
    Browser->>Discord: Redirect to OAuth2
    Discord->>Admin: Consent screen
    Admin->>Discord: Approve
    Discord->>Browser: Redirect with code
    Browser->>API: POST /api/auth/discord/callback
    API->>Discord: Exchange code for tokens
    Discord-->>API: User info (id, username)
    API->>API: Generate User JWT
    API-->>Browser: { token, user }
    Browser->>Browser: Store user JWT

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 2: Check Admin Eligibility

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Admin Portal"
    Browser->>API: GET /api/admin/check
    Note right of Browser: Authorization: Bearer <userJWT>

    API->>API: Extract discordUserId from JWT
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM admin_whitelist WHERE discord_user_id = ?

    alt User in Whitelist
        DB-->>API: Admin entry (with hasPublicKey status)
        API-->>Browser: { isAdmin: true, hasPublicKey: true, adminRole: "OWNER" }
    else Not in Whitelist
        API-->>Browser: { isAdmin: false, reason: "Not in whitelist" }
        Browser-->>Admin: Access Denied
    end

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 3: Request Challenge

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Request Challenge"
    Browser->>API: GET /api/admin/challenge

    API->>API: Generate random nonce & challengeId
    API->>API: Sign challenge with Pudel's PRIVATE key
    Note right of API: signature = RSA_SIGN(payload, pudelPrivateKey)
    API->>API: Store challenge (expires in 5 min)

    API-->>Browser: { challengeId, nonce, signature, expiry }

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 4: Verify Server Identity (Optional)

    Browser->>Browser: Verify Pudel's signature
    Note right of Browser: Using Pudel's PUBLIC key<br/>Confirms this is real Pudel server
    Browser-->>Admin: "Server Identity Verified ✓"

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 5: Sign Challenge with Admin's Private Key

    Admin->>Browser: Upload/paste private key
    Note right of Admin: Private key stays in browser!
    Browser->>Browser: RSA_SIGN(nonce, adminPrivateKey)
    Note right of Browser: Using Web Crypto API<br/>Key never transmitted
    Browser-->>Browser: signature = Base64(signedNonce)
    Browser-->>Admin: "Challenge Signed ✓"

    Note over Admin,Discord: Step 6: Submit Signed Challenge

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Complete Login"
    Browser->>API: POST /api/admin/auth/mutual
    Note right of Browser: Authorization: Bearer <userJWT><br/>Body: { challengeId, signature }

    API->>API: Validate challenge exists & not expired
    API->>API: Extract discordUserId from user JWT
    API->>DB: SELECT public_key_pem FROM admin_whitelist<br/>WHERE discord_user_id = ?
    DB-->>API: Admin's public key (PEM)

    API->>API: Load public key from PEM
    API->>API: Verify signature
    Note right of API: RSA_VERIFY(nonce, signature, adminPublicKey)

    alt Signature Valid
        API->>API: Generate AdminJWT (24-hour session)
        Note right of API: Claims: sessionId, discordUserId,<br/>adminRole, canModify, canManageAdmins
        API->>DB: UPDATE admin_whitelist SET last_login = NOW()
        API-->>Browser: { success: true, adminToken, adminRole }
        Browser->>Browser: Store adminToken
        Browser-->>Admin: Redirect to Admin Dashboard
    else Signature Invalid
        API-->>Browser: { error: "Signature verification failed" }
        Browser-->>Admin: "Authentication Failed"
    end

    Note over Admin,Discord: Admin Panel Operations (Authenticated)

    Admin->>Browser: Manage Plugins
    Browser->>API: GET /api/admin/plugins
    Note right of Browser: Authorization: Bearer <adminToken>

    API->>API: Validate AdminJWT
    API->>API: Check session & permissions

    alt Valid Admin Session
        API->>DB: Query plugin data
        DB-->>API: Plugin list
        API-->>Browser: { plugins: [...] }
        Browser-->>Admin: Display Plugin Manager
    else Invalid/Expired Session
        API-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser->>Browser: Redirect to Admin Login
    end

    Note over Admin,Discord: Logout

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Logout"
    Browser->>API: POST /api/admin/logout
    Note right of Browser: Authorization: Bearer <adminToken>
    API->>API: Invalidate session
    API-->>Browser: { success: true }
    Browser->>Browser: Clear adminToken
    Browser-->>Admin: Redirect to Home
